[Non development post]
I encountered a performance bottleneck with my new SSD and after a lot of diagnosing trials, it was for my surprise that my "Marvell SE9128 Sata 3 chipset" is the main reason :( ... If anyone of you is having a performance problems with Sata 3.0 SSDs, check your chipset first. To sum the result up for you,  Marvel is the worst.
posts.caption: techgage.com
posts.description: With newer SSDs now coming well within 10% of maxing out a SATA 3.0 port, it’s important to make sure that your motherboard is properly equipped to handle such drives if planning to buy one. posts.message: This little service converts a github repository's markdown files to a pdf file :)
posts.caption: gitprint.com
posts.description: Simply view any Markdown file on GitHub, then in your URL bar replace the github.com part of the URL with gitprint.com — your markdown file will be rendered to a beautiful, printable PDF.

posts.caption: Lean Business Planning for Startups
posts.description:
This 2 day workshop will take you step by step towards understanding the method, mastering its tools and validating your own idea.

It is a practical workshop...get ready for lots of action!

Outline:
- What is Lean Business Method?
- The difference between Lean and Business model
- How can we use both methods for maximum impact.
- How to use lean to startup?
- How to use lean to develop your business?
- How to use The experimenting board?
- Handling results.
- What are the Real tips from the real entrepreneurs.

*Your big idea will be our case study.
*out come of the workshop will be the validation of your idea/ the validation of the make over your mid aged business needs.
